data.description: This quiet, end-unit townhouse is located in a low maintenance community, ensuring that you can enjoy a hassle-free lifestyle.  The heart of the home is the open concept design which seamlessly blends the kitchen and living area, creating a welcoming space that is perfect for both relaxation and entertaining guests.  The private courtyard provides additional entertaining space for those summer BBQ's or a serene space to enjoy your morning coffee.  This home boasts a spacious primary suite, complete with a 5-piece bathroom and a convenient walk-in closet, providing the perfect retreat to unwind after a long day.  Two additional bedrooms, a second full bathroom and a dedicated laundry room complete the upstairs.  With air conditioning, you'll stay comfortable year-round, no matter the season.  This townhouse also boasts an attached 1-car garage, providing convenience and protection for your vehicle.  This low maintenance home offers an array of benefits, including its prime location near both Peterson Space Force Base and the Powers Corridor, ensuring easy access to an abundance of shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Whether you're looking to explore the great outdoors or enjoy the vibrant city life, this townhouse is ideally positioned to meet all your needs.
